@startuml
[*] --> CreateAccount : create account
CreateAccount --> [*] : registration not successful
CreateAccount --> LoggedIn : registration successful

LoggedIn --> CheckWeather : check weather
CheckWeather --> InvalidLocation : invalid location
InvalidLocation --> [*] : end process

CheckWeather --> SelectWeatherInfo : valid location
SelectWeatherInfo --> [*] : select weather info
SelectWeatherInfo --> ShowWeatherInfo : show selected weather information

ShowWeatherInfo --> ViewAdditionalDetails : view additional details
ViewAdditionalDetails --> [*] : view additional details

LoggedIn --> Logout : logout
Logout --> [*] : end session
@enduml
